Ma help garna ready chu.	Yo bill sahi chhaina hai?
Tapain ko samasya bujhna try garxu.	Bill check garera bujhna sakina.
Sodhna parcha.	Bill ma kehi milena.
Ma yasko samadhan khojna lagdai chu.	Bill ko baare ma bujhna sakina.
Tapai ko bill kasari fixed garne sanga ma ho.	Bill ma thulo problem chha.
Thik cha, ma help garxu.	Bill herera confused bhaye.
Sodhna lai samaya lagchha.	Bill milena.
Detail diyera herna parcha.	Bill maa kehi confusion chha.
Mero team ko sanga discuss garnu parcha.	Mero bill maa problem chha.
Ma check garxu ani update dinchu.	Bill ma thikai chaina jasto chha.
Hamro team yo samadhan garxa.	Bill herda milena ra disturbed bhaye.
Ma yasko samadhan khojna try garxu.	Bill ko problem kasari soltaune?
Hamro team herxa.	Yo bill herda confused lagyo.

Carbon footprint le paryawaran ma dherai hanikarak asar parcha.Fossil fuels ko products le dherai carbon footprint utpadan garchhan.Renewable energy use gari carbon footprint lai kam garna sakinchha.Company ko production process ma clean energy use garera carbon footprint kam garna sakinchha.Transportation le carbon footprint badhauna badi fossil fuels ko upayog garcha.Natural materials le sabanda kam carbon footprint utpadan garchhan.Sustainable products le carbon footprint lai kam garna madat garchhan.Carbon footprint ko impact greenhouse gas emission ko hisab garera measure garinchha.Industrial sector ma carbon footprint sabanda badha chha.Company haru green technologies ko upayog garera carbon footprint lai kam garnalai prayas garchhan.Consumer ko behavior le carbon footprint ma dherai badal parna sakchha.Carbon footprint lai monitor garna satellite imagery jasto technology haru prayog garinchha.Carbon offsetting le tree plantation ra renewable projects ko madhyam bata carbon footprint kam garcha.Environmental policies le carbon footprint lai prabhavit garcha.Public awareness campaigns le carbon footprint ko barema chetana badhauna sakinchha.Carbon footprint le climate change ma pramukh yogdan garcha.Low carbon products ko demand increase garnalai incentives ra awareness program garna sakinchha.Carbon footprint reduction ko lagi government ra private sector bata dherai initiatives chalu gareko chha.Europe, USA ra Australia ma carbon footprint ko barema karyakram chaldai chha.Carbon footprint ko prabhav lai green technologies ra sustainable practices le samadhan garna sakinchha. Carbon footprint le paryawaran ma kasto asar parcha?Kun products le dherai carbon footprint utpadan garchhan?Kasari carbon footprint lai kam garna sakinchha?Company ko production process le kasto carbon footprint chhodchha?Transportation le carbon footprint kasari badhaunchha?Kun materials le sabanda kam carbon footprint utpadan garchhan?Sustainable products le carbon footprint kasari kam garchhan?Carbon footprint ko impact kasari measure garinchha?Kun sector ma carbon footprint sabanda badha chha?Carbon footprint lai kam garnalai company haru kasari prayas garchhan?Consumer ko behavior le carbon footprint ma kasto bhumika kheldachha?Carbon footprint lai monitor garna kun technology haru prayog garinchha?Carbon offsetting le carbon footprint kasari samadhan garcha?Kun policies le carbon footprint lai prabhavit garcha?Carbon footprint ko barema chetana kasari badhauna sakinchha?Carbon footprint le climate change ma kasto yogdan garchha?Low carbon products ko demand kasari badhauna sakinchha?Carbon footprint reduction ko lagi kun initiative haru chalu gareko chha?Kun kun desh haru ma carbon footprint ko barema karyakram chaldai chha?Carbon footprint ko prabhav kasari samadhan garna sakinchha?
Carbon footprint bhaneko byakti ya samuh le utpanna gareko total greenhouse gases ho.Carbon footprint naapna kai maapdanda haru hunchhan jastai metric tons of CO2.Transportation, fossil fuels ko upayog, ra industry le carbon footprint badhaunchha.Renewable energy ko upayog ra energy efficiency le carbon footprint kam garcha.Plastic products ra single-use items le dherai carbon footprint utpanna garchha.Carbon footprint ko asar paryawaran ma global warming ra climate change ma hunchha.Carbon calculator ko madat le hamro carbon footprint ko parimad thaha pauna sakinchha.Sustainable products prakritik samagri ra renewable energy ko prayog le carbon footprint kam garcha.Daily activities ma changes, jastai public transport prayog garnu le carbon footprint kam garna sakinchha.Energy, transportation, ra industry sectors le sab bhanda dherai carbon footprint utpanna garchhan.Carbon footprint ko barema jankari dina educational campaigns ra workshops upayogi hunchha.Carbon offsetting bhaneko green projects ma invest garna ho jun le utpanna greenhouse gases kam garcha.Recycling, energy-efficient appliances, ra sustainable materials ko upayog le carbon footprint kam garcha.Online shopping le packaging materials ra delivery emissions ko karan le carbon footprint badhaunchha.Awareness programs ra media campaigns le carbon footprint ko barema janata lai chetana garna sakinchha.Electric vehicles le fossil fuels ko upayog kam gareko le carbon footprint kam garcha.Books, online courses, ra environmental websites le carbon footprint ko barema sikna sakinchha.Travel le fossil fuels ko upayog badhaune le carbon footprint ma prabhav parcha.Greenhouse gases jaise CO2 carbon footprint ko mul roop ho.Carbon footprint kam garna government niti haru ma renewable energy incentives ra strict emissions regulations chhan.	Carbon footprint bhaneko ke ho?Carbon footprint kasari naapinchha?Kun activities le carbon footprint badhaunchha?Carbon footprint kam garna ke garna sakinchha?Kun products le dherai carbon footprint utpanna garchha?Carbon footprint ko asar paryawaran ma kasari parcha?Kasari thaha pauna sakinchha hamro carbon footprint kati chha?Sustainable products le carbon footprint kasari kam garcha?Carbon footprint kam garna ko lagi ke ke steps lina sakinchha?Kun industries le sab bhanda dherai carbon footprint utpanna garchhan?Carbon footprint ko barema janaune sahi tarika k ho?Carbon offsetting bhaneko ke ho?Carbon footprint ko pratibad ko lagi kun kun samagri prayog garna parcha?Online shopping le carbon footprint kasari badhaunchha?Kasari carbon footprint ko barema janata lai chetana garna sakinchha?Electric vehicles le carbon footprint ma kasto asar parcha?Carbon footprint ko barema sikne uttam srot haru kun kun hun?Kasari travel le carbon footprint ma prabhav parcha?Greenhouse gases ra carbon footprint ko sambandha ke ho?Carbon footprint ko pratibad ko lagi kun kun government niti haru chha?
Carbon footprint bhaneko byakti ya samuh le utpanna gareko total greenhouse gases ho.Carbon footprint naapna kai maapdanda haru hunchhan jastai metric tons of CO2.Transportation, fossil fuels ko upayog, ra industry le carbon footprint badhaunchha.Renewable energy ko upayog ra energy efficiency le carbon footprint kam garcha.Plastic products ra single-use items le dherai carbon footprint utpanna garchha.Carbon footprint ko asar paryawaran ma global warming ra climate change ma hunchha.Carbon calculator ko madat le hamro carbon footprint ko parimad thaha pauna sakinchha.Sustainable products prakritik samagri ra renewable energy ko prayog le carbon footprint kam garcha.Daily activities ma changes, jastai public transport prayog garnu le carbon footprint kam garna sakinchha.Energy, transportation, ra industry sectors le sab bhanda dherai carbon footprint utpanna garchhan.Carbon footprint ko barema jankari dina educational campaigns ra workshops upayogi hunchha.Carbon offsetting bhaneko green projects ma invest garna ho jun le utpanna greenhouse gases kam garcha.Recycling, energy-efficient appliances, ra sustainable materials ko upayog le carbon footprint kam garcha.Online shopping le packaging materials ra delivery emissions ko karan le carbon footprint badhaunchha.Awareness programs ra media campaigns le carbon footprint ko barema janata lai chetana garna sakinchha.Electric vehicles le fossil fuels ko upayog kam gareko le carbon footprint kam garcha.Books, online courses, ra environmental websites le carbon footprint ko barema sikna sakinchha.Travel le fossil fuels ko upayog badhaune le carbon footprint ma prabhav parcha.Greenhouse gases jaise CO2 carbon footprint ko mul roop ho.Carbon footprint kam garna government niti haru ma renewable energy incentives ra strict emissions regulations chhan. Eco-friendly packaging bhaneko paryawaran mitra packaging ho.Eco-friendly packaging ko materials ma bamboo, recycled paper, ra biodegradable plastics parchan.Eco-friendly packaging banauna sakinchha prakritik samagri haru prayog gari.Eco-friendly packaging le paryawaran ma sakaratmak asar parcha.Eco-friendly packaging ko upayog chetana ra suchana marfat badhauna sakinchha.Eco-friendly packaging aru packaging bhanda ramro chha kinaki yo paryawaran lai kam asar garcha.Yes, ma eco-friendly packaging chus garchhu.Eco-friendly packaging ko cost thulo parcha tara yesko fayda dherai chha.Bahulai company haru eco-friendly packaging use garchhan jastai Amazon, IKEA, ra Patagonia.Eco-friendly packaging asani sanga recycle garna sakinchha.Eco-friendly packaging ko lifespan short-term chha.Eco-friendly packaging le energy consumption kamai dinchha.Eco-friendly packaging attractive designs ra eco-label le consumer lai attract garcha.Bamboo ra recycled paper sabai bhanda ramro eco-friendly packaging banauna upayogi hunchha.Eco-friendly packaging ko market trend growing chha.Eco-friendly packaging sustainable chha kinaki yesle kam pollution garcha.Europe ra North America ma eco-friendly packaging ko demand badhiraheko chha.Yes, malaai eco-friendly packaging ko barema ramro janakari chha.Eco-friendly packaging le carbon footprint kamai dinchha.Yes, ma eco-friendly packaging ko faida ma viswas garchhu. Recycling program ko barema mero bichar sakaratmak chha.Plastic, paper, glass, ra metal recycling program ma include hunchhan.Recycling program le materials lai feri naya banai dinchha.Recycling program le environment ma sakaratmak asar parcha.Recycling program lai sahaj banauna community participation jaruri chha.Germany, Sweden, ra South Korea ma recycling program safal bhaeko chha.Recycling program ko cost thap thap materials ma dependent hunchha.Recycling program ko labh sabai lai parda chha, society, economy ra environment.Recycling program lai aroha garna government incentives upayogi hunchha.Recycling program ko awareness campaigns ra educational programs marfat failauna sakinchha.Recycling program le carbon footprint kam garna madat garchha.Plastic bottles ra aluminum cans sabai bhanda besi recycle garinchan.Recycling program ma logistics ra cost allocation challenges face garnu parcha.Recycling program ko upayog consumer awareness ra accessibility badhauna sakinchha.Tesla ra Apple jasta companies le effective recycling program operate garchhan.Recycling program le economic growth ma resource efficiency ra job creation marfat madat garchha.Recycling program le recycling centers ra waste management industry ma job opportunities create garchha.Schools ra colleges ma recycling bins ra educational sessions marfat recycling program implement garna sakinchha.Government policies jasta ki waste management regulations le recycling program support garchha.Recycling program ko future potential dherai bright chha, sustainable development ko lagi. Recycling program le paryawaran sudharna sakchha.Plastic, glass, paper, ani metal jasta chij haru recycling garnu milchha.Recycling program ko dherai labh haru chhan, jasle paryawaran sudharcha.Jagrukta ani sahi nirdeshan le recycling program lai saphal banauna sakinchha.Germany ra Japan ma saphal recycling program chalan ma chhan.Recycling ko prakriya materials ko collection, sorting, processing ani remanufacturing ho.Recycling program le manufacturing, construction, ani daily life ma asar garchha.Awareness campaigns le recycling program ko jagrukta badhauna sakchha.Paper ani aluminum cans sabai bhanda dherai recycle garincha.Community centers ani drop-off locations ma sahabhagi huna sakchha.Prashasan ko sahi niti ani sahayog recycling program ko lagi jaruri chha.Recycling le raw materials ko upayog kam garna sakchha.Recycling program le rojgariko avasar banaunda sakchha.Advanced sorting technology recycling program ko lagi prayog garincha.Recycling program le community ko cleanliness ra health ma madat garchha.Recycling program le energy ko bachaat garchha.Recycling program ko lagi sustainable niti banaiyeko chha.Recycling program le garbage management sudharna sakchha.Plastic bottles, paper, glass containers ani metal cans recycle garnu parchha.Recycling program le future generations ko lagi clean environment banaunda sakchha. Yesle mero expectation anusar kam gareko cha.	Yo product le tapain ko asha anusar kam gareko cha?

Sanchai rahos, pheri bhetchau.	Pheri bhetchau, sanchai rahos.

Sanchai chu, dhanyabad.	Namaste, tapai kasto hunuhuncha?
Ramrai cha, tapai sanchai hunuhuncha?	Namaste, hajur ko din kasto cha?
Mero mood thik cha, hajur ko kasto cha?	Namaste, tapai ko mood kasto cha?
Mero din thik cha, hajur ko kasto cha?	Namaste, tapai lai bhetera ramailo lagyo.
Sabai thik chha, tapai lai?	Namaste, ke chha khabar?
Thik cha, tapai ko yojana ke cha?	Namaste, tapai sanchai hunuhuncha?
Thik cha, ajako din kasto chaliraheko cha?	Namaste, ajako yojana ke cha?
Ramrai cha, tapai ko din kasto cha?	Namaste, tapai ko diwas kasari suru bhayo?
Thik cha, tapai ko bihan kasto cha?	Namaste, tapai ko bihan kasto bhayo?
Ramrai cha, hajur ko din kasto suru bhayo?	Namaste, tapai le bihan ke bhojnu bhayo?
Mero raat thik bhayo, hajur ko?	Namaste, hajur ko raat kasto bhayo?
Sanchai chhu, hajur lai?	Namaste, tapai ke garnu huncha?
Ramrai cha, tapai le bihan ke bhojnu bhayo?	Namaste, tapai ko raat kasto bitayo?
Mero mood thik cha, tapai ko?	Namaste, tapai lai ramailo lagyo?
Ramro cha, hajur ko mood kasto cha?	Namaste, hajur ko din kasto bitiraheko cha?
Sanchai chhu, hajur ko yojana ke cha?	Namaste, hajur ko yojana ke cha?
Thik cha, hajur ko subha diwas kasto cha?	Namaste, tapai sanchai hunuhuncha?
Mero diwas thik bhayo, tapai ko?	Namaste, hajur ko diwas kasto cha?
Thik cha, hajur ko yatra kasto bhayo?	Namaste, tapai ko yatra kasto bhayo?
Ramrai cha, tapai ko diwas kasto bhayo?	Namaste, tapai ko subha diwas kasto cha?

Sanchai chhu, hajur lai?	Namaste, tapai ke garnu huncha?
Ramrai cha, tapai le bihan ke bhojnu bhayo?	Namaste, tapai ko raat kasto bitayo?
Mero mood thik cha, tapai ko?	Namaste, tapai lai ramailo lagyo?
Ramro cha, hajur ko mood kasto cha?	Namaste, hajur ko din kasto bitiraheko cha?
Sanchai chhu, hajur ko yojana ke cha?	Namaste, hajur ko yojana ke cha?
Thik cha, hajur ko subha diwas kasto cha?	Namaste, tapai sanchai hunuhuncha?

Tapainle hamro loyalty program bata dherai points pauna saknuhunchha.	Tapainko loyalty program bata maile dherai points kasari pauna sakchhu?

Tapain hamro loyalty program ma points kamau na saknuhunchha.	Tapainko loyalty program ma points kamau na ma ke garnu sakchhu?
Hamro loyalty program ma points kamau na, tapainle hamro website ma kinmel garnu saknuhunchha.	Malaai asha chha, tapainko loyalty program ma kasari points kamau na sakchhu?
Points kamau na ko lagi, kripaya hamro website ma bibhinna utpadan haru kinmel garnuhos.	Malaai points kamau na ko lagi ke garnu parchha?

Tapainle harek kinmel ma points prapt garnu saknuhunchha.	Tapainko loyalty program ma points kasari milchha?

Hamro sadasyata taharu dherai chhan.	Tapainko sadasyata taharu kati chhan?

Tapai le kinmel garera points kamauna saknu huncha.	Maile points kasari kamauna sakchhu?
Harek kinmel ma points paunu huncha.	Points kamauna k garne?

Tapainko order ma aru items add garna milchha. Kripaya, order modification section ma janu hos ra items add garne option chunu hos.	Maile gareko order ma aru items add garna milchha?
Order ma naya item add garna ko lagi order modification section ma janu hos ra items add garne button chunu hos.	Order ma naya item add garna kasari garne?
Tapainko order ma aru items add garna milchha. Order modification section ma janu hos ra items add garne option chunu hos.	Order ma aru item add garnu parcha.
Order place garepachi pani item add garna milchha. Kripaya, order modification section ma janu hos ra items add garne option chunu hos.	Maile order place garepachi item add garna sakchhu?
Order ma aru items add garna milchha. Kripaya, order modification section ma janu hos ra items add garne option chunu hos.	Order ma aru items kasari add garna milchha?
Order ma naya item add garna sakchhu. Kripaya, order modification section ma janu hos ra items add garne option chunu hos.	Order ma naya item add garna chaahanchu.
Order ma add garna milne items ko barema janakari order modification section bata pau.	Order ma add garna milne items k ho?
Order ma aru items samavesh garna milchha. Kripaya, order modification section ma janu hos ra items add garne option chunu hos.	Order ma aru items samavesh garna kasari garne?

Chinta nagarnuhos. Tapainko order bata item haru hatauna sakincha. Kripaya grahak sewama sampark garnuhos ra uniharu le tapailai maddat garnechan.	Maile galti garera badi item order garechu, ke garne?
Ho, tapainko order bata euta item hatauna sambhav cha. Kripaya hamro grahak sewa number ma call garnuhos ra hami tapailai sahayog garnechau.	Mero order bata euta item hatauna milcha?
Ho, order garisakepachi pani saman ghatauna sakincha. Kripaya hamro website ma login garnuhos ra 'Order Modify' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos.	Order garisakepachi saman ghatauna sakincha?
Chinta nagarnuhos. Dohoro order radd garna hamro grahak sewa toli lai sampark garnuhos. Uniharu le tapailai prakriya bataunechan.	Maile bhulvash dohoro order garechu, kasari radd garne?
Ho, tapainko order bata chijharu hatauna sambhav cha. Kripaya hamro mobile app ma januhos ra 'Order Sampaadan' vikalpa prayog garnuhos.	Ke mero order bata kehi chijharu hatauna sambhav cha?
Kunai chinta linu pardaina. Tapaile chahanubhayeko saman hatauna hamro website ma gai 'Order Vyavasthapan' prishtha ma januhos.	Maile order gareko euta saman chahidaina, ke garnuparcha?
Ho, order gareko saman firta garna milcha. Kripaya hamro firti niti hernuhos ra tyaspachi grahak sewa ma sampark garnuhos.	Order gareko saman firta garna milcha?
Chinta nagarnuhos. Tapainko order sachyauna hamro helpline ma call garnuhos. Hami tapailai maddat garna tayar chhau.	Mero order ma galti bhayo, kasari sachyaune?
Ho, order modify garna milcha. Kripaya hamro website ma login garera 'Mero Order haru' ma januhos ra tyaha sampaadan garna saknuhunecha.	Ke order modify garna milcha?
Order bata vastu hataune prakriya saral cha. Hamro mobile app kholnuhos, order chhanot garnuhos, ra 'Item Hataunuhos' ma click garnuhos.	Order bata vastu hataune prakriya kasto cha?
Chinta nagarnuhos. Tapaile chahanubhayeko saman hatauna hamro grahak sewa number ma call garnuhos. Hami tapailai maddat garnechau.	Maile order gareko kehi saman chahidaina, ke garne?
Ho, order garisakepachi pani saman hatauna milcha. Kripaya hamro website ma januhos ra 'Order Vyavasthapan' prishtha ma gai prakriya pura garnuhos.	Order garisakepachi pani saman hatauna milcha?
Ho, tapainko order ma parivartan garna sakincha. Kripaya hamro mobile app ma login garnuhos ra 'Order Sampaadan' vikalpa prayog garnuhos.	Mero order ma parivartan garna sakincha?
Order bata saman hatauda samanyataya shulka lagdaina. Tara kripaya hamro niti janchnuhos va thap jankaari ko lagi grahak sewa ma sampark garnuhos.	Order bata saman hatauda shulka lagcha?
Chinta nagarnuhos. Dherai saman hatauna hamro helpline ma call garnuhos. Hamro toli le tapailai sahayog garnecha.	Maile galtile dherai saman order garechu, aba ke garne?
Ho, tapainko order bata item hatauna sakincha. Kripaya hamro website ma januhos ra 'Mero Order haru' khand ma gai sampaadan garnuhos.	Ke mero order bata item hatauna sakincha?
Order modify garne prakriya saral cha. Hamro mobile app kholnuhos, order chhanot garnuhos, ra 'Sampaadan garnuhos' ma click garnuhos.	Order modify garne prakriya kasto cha?
Ho, tapainko order bata euta vastu hatauna sambhav cha. Kripaya hamro website ma login garera 'Order Vyavasthapan' prishtha ma januhos.	Mero order bata euta vastu hatauna chahanchu, sambhav cha?
Ho, order garisakepachi saman hatauna milcha. Kripaya hamro grahak sewa number ma call garnuhos ra hami tapailai maddat garnechau.	Order garisakepachi saman hatauna milcha ki mildaina?
Saman firta garna hamro website ma januhos ra 'Firti Prakriya' prishtha ma nirdeshanharu palana garnuhos. Kunai samasya bhaye hamilai call garnuhos.	Maile order gareko kehi saman firta garna chahanchu, kasari garne?
Chinta nagarnuhos. Tapainko order bata item haru hatauna sakincha. Kripaya grahak sewama sampark garnuhos ra uniharu le tapailai maddat garnechan.	Maile galti garera badi item order garechu, ke garne?
Ho, tapainko order bata euta item hatauna sambhav cha. Kripaya hamro grahak sewa number ma call garnuhos ra hami tapailai sahayog garnechau.	Mero order bata euta item hatauna milcha?
Ho, order garisakepachi pani saman ghatauna sakincha. Kripaya hamro website ma login garnuhos ra 'Order Modify' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos.	Order garisakepachi saman ghatauna sakincha?
Chinta nagarnuhos. Dohoro order radd garna hamro grahak sewa toli lai sampark garnuhos. Uniharu le tapailai prakriya bataunechan.	Maile bhulvash dohoro order garechu, kasari radd garne?
Ho, tapainko order bata chijharu hatauna sambhav cha. Kripaya hamro mobile app ma januhos ra 'Order Sampaadan' vikalpa prayog garnuhos.	Ke mero order bata kehi chijharu hatauna sambhav cha?
Kunai chinta linu pardaina. Tapaile chahanubhayeko saman hatauna hamro website ma gai 'Order Vyavasthapan' prishtha ma januhos.	Maile order gareko euta saman chahidaina, ke garnuparcha?
Ho, order gareko saman firta garna milcha. Kripaya hamro firti niti hernuhos ra tyaspachi grahak sewa ma sampark garnuhos.	Order gareko saman firta garna milcha?
Chinta nagarnuhos. Tapainko order sachyauna hamro helpline ma call garnuhos. Hami tapailai maddat garna tayar chhau.	Mero order ma galti bhayo, kasari sachyaune?
Ho, order modify garna milcha. Kripaya hamro website ma login garera 'Mero Order haru' ma januhos ra tyaha sampaadan garna saknuhunecha.	Ke order modify garna milcha?
Order bata vastu hataune prakriya saral cha. Hamro mobile app kholnuhos, order chhanot garnuhos, ra 'Item Hataunuhos' ma click garnuhos.	Order bata vastu hataune prakriya kasto cha?
Chinta nagarnuhos. Tapaile chahanubhayeko saman hatauna hamro grahak sewa number ma call garnuhos. Hami tapailai maddat garnechau.	Maile order gareko kehi saman chahidaina, ke garne?
Ho, order garisakepachi pani saman hatauna milcha. Kripaya hamro website ma januhos ra 'Order Vyavasthapan' prishtha ma gai prakriya pura garnuhos.	Order garisakepachi pani saman hatauna milcha?
Ho, tapainko order ma parivartan garna sakincha. Kripaya hamro mobile app ma login garnuhos ra 'Order Sampaadan' vikalpa prayog garnuhos.	Mero order ma parivartan garna sakincha?
Order bata saman hatauda samanyataya shulka lagdaina. Tara kripaya hamro niti janchnuhos va thap jankaari ko lagi grahak sewa ma sampark garnuhos.	Order bata saman hatauda shulka lagcha?
Chinta nagarnuhos. Dherai saman hatauna hamro helpline ma call garnuhos. Hamro toli le tapailai sahayog garnecha.	Maile galtile dherai saman order garechu, aba ke garne?

Tapaiko chinta samadhan garna hamro order cancel garne niyam yasto cha.	Order cancel garne niyam ma kasto chinta cha?
Cancel policy ko bare ma yo jankari cha, tapaiko chinta samadhan huncha.	Cancel policy bare bistar ma janakari dinus, ma chintit chu.
Order cancel garnu parda yasto process huncha, tapaiko chinta samadhan garna.	Order cancel garnu parda kasto process huncha? Ma chintit chu.
Hamro cancel policy yo ho, tapaiko chinta samadhan huncha.	Cancel policy ke ho? Kripaya bistar ma bataidinus.
Order cancel garnu parne condition haru yasto cha, tapaiko chinta samadhan garna.	Order cancel garnu parne condition haru ke ke hun? Ma chintit chu.
Cancel garne niyam yasto cha, tapaiko chinta samadhan huncha.	Cancel garne niyam kasto huncha? Kripaya spashta banaidinuhos.
Order cancel garne rules haru yasto cha, tapaiko chinta samadhan garna.	Order cancel garne rules haru k k hun? Ma dherai chintit chu.
Cancel policy yasto kaam garcha, tapaiko chinta samadhan huncha.	Cancel policy kasari kaam garcha? Kripaya bujhna sahayog garnuhos.

Order cancel garne process yasto huncha, tapaiko chinta samadhan garna.	Order cancel garne process kasari huncha? Ma chintit chu.
Cancel policy ko bare ma thap jankari yo cha, tapaiko chinta samadhan huncha.	Cancel policy ko bare ma thap janakari dinus, ma chintit chu.
Order cancel garnu parda yo garnu parcha, tapaiko chinta samadhan garna.	Order cancel garnu parda ke ke garnu parcha? Ma chintit chu.
Cancel policy lai yasto follow garnu parcha, tapaiko chinta samadhan huncha.	Cancel policy lai kasari follow garne? Ma chintit chu.
Order cancel garnu parne condition haru yasto huncha, tapaiko chinta samadhan garna.	Order cancel garnu parne condition k k huncha? Kripaya spashta banaidinuhos.

Tapai ko website ma 'rating dinuhos' buttonma click gareyo bhane bistrit rating prakriya suru garna saknuhunchha.	Tapai ko website ma yo utpadanko bistrit rating dine prakriya kasto chha?
5 ma 3 tara din ra yas ko karan batanna tapai le hamro website ma gayara rating formma bistrit rupma lekhnuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko 5 ma 3 tara din chahanchu ra yo kin din chahanchu bhanera bistrit rupma batanna chahanchu. Kasari garum?

Tapai ko website ma 'rating dinuhos' bikalpako khoji garnuhos ra tyaha click garnuhos.	Tapai ko website ma yo utpadanko bistrit rating dine bikalpa kaha chha?

Sakaratmak pakshako bistrit samiksha din tapai le utpadanko ramro pakshaharu bistrit rupma ulek gari rating dinuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko sakaratmak pakshako bistrit samiksha garna chahanchu. Kasari rating dine?
Sabai bhanda sajilo tarika bhane ko hamro website ma gayara 'rating dinuhos' ma click garnu ho.	Ke tapai malai yo utpadanko bistrit rating dine sabai bhanda sajilo tarika batanna saknuhunchha?
Tapai ko website ma 'rating dinuhos' bikalpako khoji garnuhos ra tyaha click garnuhos.	Tapai ko website ma yo utpadanko bistrit rating dine bikalpa kaha chha?
5 tara din ra bistrit samiksha din tapai le 'rating dinuhos' ma gayara 5 tara chayan garnuhos ra bistrit rupma lekhnuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko 5 tara din chahanchu ra bistrit samiksha din chahanchu. Kasari garum?
Naya bistrit rating dine bikalpa hamro website ma 'rating dinuhos' ma upalabdha chha.	Tapai ko website ma yo utpadanko bistrit rating dine sabai bhanda naya bikalpa kasto chha?
1 tara din ra yas ko karan batanna tapai le 'rating dinuhos' ma gayara 1 tara chayan garnuhos ra bistrit rupma lekhnuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko 1 tara din chahanchu ra bistrit rupma kin din chahanchu bhanera batanna chahanchu. Kasari garum?
Sabai bhanda prabhavkari tarika bhane ko imandar ra spashta pratikriya dinu ho.	Ke tapai malai yo utpadanko bistrit rupma rating dine sabai bhanda prabhavkari tarika batanna saknuhunchha?
Nispaksha rupma bistrit samiksha din tapai le imandar samikshako sath rating garnuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko harek pakshako nispaksha rupma samiksha kasari garna sakchhu?
Tapai hamro website ma gayara 'rating dinuhos' bikalpa ma click gareyo bhane yo utpadanko bistrit rating din saknuhunchha.	Ma yo utpadanko rating din chahanchu. Prakriya ke ho?
Ho, tapai yo utpadanko pratyek pakshako samiksha garna saknuhunchha. Hamro website ma samiksha lekhne form bharidinuhos.	Ke ma yo utpadanko pratyek pakshako samiksha garna sakchhu?
Yo utpadanko gunastarko bistrit bisleshan garna tapai le hamro website ma gayara 'rating dinuhos' ma click garna saknuhunchha.	Ma yo utpadanko gunastarko bistrit bisleshan garna chahanchu. Kasari rating dine?
Yo utpadanko bisesta haruko adharma rating din tapai le spashta ra bistrit pratikriya dinuhos.	Tapai malai yo utpadanko bisesta haruko adharma rating din ko lagi sujhab din saknuhunchha?
Faida ra befaida ulek garera tapai le bistrit rupma rating din saknuhunchha. Hamro website ma rating formma janu hos.	Ma yo utpadanko faida ra befaidako bistrit samiksha garna chahanchu. Kasari rating dine?
Tapai ko website ma 'rating dinuhos' buttonma click gareyo bhane bistrit rating prakriya suru garna saknuhunchha.	Tapai ko website ma yo utpadanko bistrit rating dine prakriya kasto chha?
5 ma 3 tara din ra yas ko karan batanna tapai le hamro website ma gayara rating formma bistrit rupma lekhnuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko 5 ma 3 tara din chahanchu ra yo kin din chahanchu bhanera bistrit rupma batanna chahanchu. Kasari garum?
Tapai le utpadanko harek pakshako samiksha garne samaya bistrit rupma dinu upayukta hunchha.	Ke tapai malai yo utpadanko harek pakshako samiksha garna ko lagi sifaris garna saknuhunchha?
Tapai le 'rating dinuhos' buttonma click gareyo bhane bistrit rating prakriya suru garna saknuhunchha.	Yo utpadanko bistrit rupma rating dine vidhi kasto chha?
Samiksha lekhera ra bistrit rating din tapai le hamro website ma rating form bharinuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko harek pakshako imandar samiksha kasari garna sakchhu?

Sakaratmak samiksha din tapai le utpadanko ramro pakh haru ullekh gardai rating dinuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko sakaratmak samiksha din chahanchu. Kasari rating dine?
Sabai bhanda sajilo tarika bhane ko hamro website ma gayara 'rating dinuhos' ma click garnu ho.	Ke tapai malai yo utpadanko rating dine sabai bhanda sajilo tarika batanna saknuhunchha?
Tapai ko website ma 'rating dinuhos' bikalpako khoji garnuhos ra tyaha click garnuhos.	Tapai ko website ma yo utpadanko rating dine bikalpa kaha chha?
5 tara din tapai le 'rating dinuhos' ma gayara 5 tara chayan garnuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko 5 tara din chahanchu. Kasari garum?
Naya rating dine bikalpa hamro website ma 'rating dinuhos' ma upalabdha chha.	Tapai ko website ma yo utpadanko rating dine sabai bhanda naya bikalpa kasto chha?
1 tara din tapai le 'rating dinuhos' ma gayara 1 tara chayan garnuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko 1 tara din chahanchu. Kasari garum?
Sabai bhanda prabhavkari tarika bhane ko imandar ra spashta pratikriya dinu ho.	Ke tapai malai yo utpadanko rating dine sabai bhanda prabhavkari tarika batanna saknuhunchha?
Nispaksha rupma rating din tapai le imandar samikshako sath rating garnuhos.	Ma yo utpadanko nispaksha rupma kasari rating din sakchhu?
Tapai hamro website ma gayara 'rating dinuhos' bikalpa ma click gareyo bhane yo utpadanko rating din saknuhunchha.	Ma yo utpadanko rating din chahanchu. Prakriya ke ho?
Ho, tapai imandar samiksha din saknuhunchha. Hamro website ma samiksha lekhne form bharidinuhos.	Ke ma yo utpadanko imandar samiksha din sakchhu?

Yo utpadanko rating dine samaya tapai le spashta ra imandar pratikriya dinuhos.	Ke tapai malai yo utpadanko rating din ka lagi kunai sujhab din saknuhunchha?

Utpadanko review lekhna ko lagi, kripaya hamro website ma login garnuhos ra 'review lekhnuhos' vikalpa channu hos.	Maile halai kineko utpadanko review lekhna chahanchu, ma kasari suru garnu sakchhu?
Review lekhna ko lagi, tapai le utpadanko gunastara, pradarshan, ra upayogita jasta kuraharu samavesh garnu parchha.	Review lekhna ko lagi malai ke jankari chahinchha?
Utpadanko review lekhna ko lagi prakriya sajilo chha, kripaya website ma login garera 'review lekhnuhos' button click garnuhos.	Utpadanko review lekhna ko lagi prakriya ke chha?
Review lekhdai utpadanko gunastara, mulya, ra prayog anubhavko barema bistrit jankari dinuhos.	Review lekhna ko lagi ke ke kurama dhyan dinu parchha?
Lekheko review prakatit hun samanyata 2-3 din lagna sakchha.	Maile lekheko review prakatit hun kati samaya lagchha?
Utpadanko bistrit review lekhna ko lagi, tapai le utpadanko sabai pakshaharuko barema lekhnu parchha.	Utpadanko bistrit review kasari lekhna sakchhu?
Review lekhdai, utpadanko gunastara, mulya, ra pradarshan jasta kuraharu samavesh garnuhos.	Review lekhdai ke kuraharu samavesh garnu parchha?
Review lekhna ko lagi kunai bishesh dishanirdesh chhaina, tara tapai le utpadanko bastabik anubhav lekhnu hos.	Review lekhna ko lagi ke kunai bishesh dishanirdesh chhan?
Review lekhi sakepachi tapai le review sampadan garnu sakchhu.	Maile review lekhi sakepachi ke ma sampadan garnu sakchhu?
Review lekhdai utpadanko upayogita ra pradarshan ko barema bistrit bibaran dinuhos.	Review lekhdai ke kuraharu le ramro prabhav parchha?
Tapai le lekheko review aru grahakharu le pani herna sakchhan.	Maile lekheko review arule pani herna sakchhan?
Review lekhna ko lagi namuna upalabdha chhaina, tara tapai le afno anubhav lekhnu hos.	Review lekhna ko lagi kunai namuna upalabdha chha?
Review lekhdai, kripaya utpadanko gunastara, mulya, ra upayogitako barema lekhnu hos.	Review lekhdai ke kurama dhyan dinu parchha?
Review lekhdai utpadanko sabai bisheshatahru ullekh garnuhos.	Review lekhdai utpadanko kun kun bisheshatahru ullekh garnu parchha?
Review lekhna ko lagi saral ra spast bhasha prayog garnuhos.	Review lekhna ko lagi kun prakarko bhasha prayog garnu parchha?
Review lekhdai utpadanko bastabik anubhav lekhnu hos.	Review lekhdai malai ke dhyan dinu parchha?
Review lekhdai, tapai le photoharu pani upload garnu sakchhu.	Review lekhdai ke ma photoharu pani upload garnu sakchhu?
Review lekhdai utpadanko gunastara, mulya, ra pradarshan jasta kuraharu ma dhyan dinuhos.	Review lekhdai ke ke kurama dhyan dinu parchha?
Review lekhdai utpadanko upayogita ra pradarshan ko barema bistrit bibaran dinuhos.	Review lekhdai ke kuraharu le ramro prabhav parchha?
Review lekhdai, kripaya utpadanko bastabik anubhav lekhnu hos.	Review lekhdai ke kurama dhyan dinu parchha?
Utpadanko review lekhna ko lagi, kripaya hamro website ma login garnuhos ra 'review lekhnuhos' vikalpa channu hos.	Maile halai kineko utpadanko review lekhna chahanchu, ma kasari suru garnu sakchhu?
Review lekhna ko lagi, tapai le utpadanko gunastara, pradarshan, ra upayogita jasta kuraharu samavesh garnu parchha.	Review lekhna ko lagi malai ke jankari chahinchha?
Utpadanko review lekhna ko lagi prakriya sajilo chha, kripaya website ma login garera 'review lekhnuhos' button click garnuhos.	Utpadanko review lekhna ko lagi prakriya ke chha?
Review lekhdai utpadanko gunastara, mulya, ra prayog anubhavko barema bistrit jankari dinuhos.	Review lekhna ko lagi ke ke kurama dhyan dinu parchha?
Lekheko review prakatit hun samanyata 2-3 din lagna sakchha.	Maile lekheko review prakatit hun kati samaya lagchha?
Utpadanko bistrit review lekhna ko lagi, tapai le utpadanko sabai pakshaharuko barema lekhnu parchha.	Utpadanko bistrit review kasari lekhna sakchhu?
Review lekhdai, utpadanko gunastara, mulya, ra pradarshan jasta kuraharu samavesh garnuhos.	Review lekhdai ke kuraharu samavesh garnu parchha?
Review lekhna ko lagi kunai bishesh dishanirdesh chhaina, tara tapai le utpadanko bastabik anubhav lekhnu hos.	Review lekhna ko lagi ke kunai bishesh dishanirdesh chhan?
Review lekhi sakepachi tapai le review sampadan garnu sakchhu.	Maile review lekhi sakepachi ke ma sampadan garnu sakchhu?
Review lekhdai utpadanko upayogita ra pradarshan ko barema bistrit bibaran dinuhos.	Review lekhdai ke kuraharu le ramro prabhav parchha?
Tapai le lekheko review aru grahakharu le pani herna sakchhan.	Maile lekheko review arule pani herna sakchhan?

Review lekhdai, kripaya utpadanko bastabik anubhav lekhnu hos.	Review lekhdai ke kurama dhyan dinu parchha?
Tapaile kineko samanko samiksha lekhna, kripaya hamro website ma login garnuhos ra utpadan prishtha ma gayera 'Samiksha Lekhnus' button ma click garnuhos.	Maile kineko samanko samiksha kasari lekhne?
Tapainko anubhav sajha garna hamro mobile app ma januhos, utpadan khojnuhos ra 'Samiksha Lekhnus' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos.	Utpadanko barema mero anubhav kaha sajha garna sakchu?
Grahak samiksha lekhna, utpadan prishtha ma januhos, tala scroll garnuhos ra 'Aafno Anubhav Sajha Garnuhos' ma click garnuhos. Tyaspachi form bharnuhos.	Grahak samiksha lekhne prakriya ke ho?
Tapaile kineko vastuko pratikriya dina, hamro website ma 'Mero Kharid haru' khand ma januhos ra sambandhi utpadanko chheu ma 'Samiksha Lekhnus' ma click garnuhos.	Maile kineko vastuko barema pratikriya kasari dine?
Utpadanko rating ra samiksha lekhna, utpadan prishtha ma januhos ra 'Samiksha Lekhnus' button khojnuhos. Tyaha tapaile tara rating dina ra aafno bichar lekhna saknuhuncha.	Utpadanko rating ra samiksha kaha lekhna sakincha?
Arulai samanko barema batauna, hamro platform ma samiksha lekhnus. Yasle anya grahak haru lai utpadanko barema janna maddat garnecha.	Maile kineko samanko barema arulai kasari bataune?
Website ma product review lekhna, utpadan prishtha ma januhos, 'Samiksha Lekhnus' ma click garnuhos, ra aafno anubhav, rating ra tippani haru lekhnus.	Website ma product review kasari lekhne?
Tapainko kinmel anubhav sajha garna, hamro website wa app ma 'Grahak Samiksha' khand ma januhos ra tyaha aafno pratikriya lekhnus.	Mero kinmelko anubhav sajha garna chahanchu, kaha garne?
Utpadanko gunstar bare aafno bichar byakta garna, utpadan prishtha ma gayera 'Samiksha Lekhnus' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos ra imandari purwak aafno anubhav lekhnus.	Utpadanko gunstarko barema mero bichar kasari byakta garne?
Grahak pratikriya form bharna hamro website ko 'Grahak Sahayata' khand ma januhos ra tyaha 'Pratikriya Dinus' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos.	Grahak pratikriya form kaha bharne?
Photo sahitko samiksha post garna, samiksha lekhda 'Photo Upload Garnuhos' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos ra aafno photo sanglagna garnuhos.	Maile kineko samanko photo sahitko samiksha kasari post garne?
Utpadanko sakaratmak ra nakaratmak paksha haru lekhna, samiksha form ma 'Faida haru' ra 'Kami haru' khand ma aafna bichar haru lekhnus.	Utpadanko sakaratmak ra nakaratmak pakshharu kaha lekhna sakchu?
Online store ma product review lekhna, aafno khata ma login garnuhos, kineko utpadan khojnuhos, ra 'Samiksha Lekhnus' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos.	Online store ma product review lekhne tarika ke ho?
Imandar pratikriya dina, utpadanko ramro ra naramro duwai paksha haru ullekh garnuhos. Tapainko wastawik anubhav sajha garnuhos.	Mero kharid anubhavko barema imandar pratikriya kasari dine?
Tapainko sujhav lekhna, utpadan prishtha ma 'Samiksha Lekhnus' ma click garnuhos ra 'Sudhar ka lagi sujhav haru' khand ma aafna bichar haru lekhnus.	Utpadanko barema mero sujhav kaha lekhna sakchu?
Samiksha lekhda utpadanko gunstar, mulya, prayogita ra tikau pana jasta paksha haru ma dhyan dinuhos. Tapainko wastawik anubhav sajha garnuhos.	Grahak samiksha lekhda ke ke kurama dhyan dinuparcha?
Utpadanko rating dina, samiksha form ma diyeko tara pranali prayog garnuhos. 1 dekhi 5 tara samma chhanot garna saknuhuncha.	Maile kineko samanko rating kasari dine?
Tapainko bichar aru sanga baadna, samiksha lekhnu ka saathai samajik media ma pani sajha garna saknuhuncha. Hamro platform bata sidhai share garne vikalpa chhanot garnuhos.	Utpadanko barema mero bichar arusanga kasari baadne?
Samiksha ma utpadanko bisheshata haru, prayog anubhav, gunstar, mulya ko uchitata ra samagra santushti samavesh garnuhos.	Samiksha lekhda kun kun jankari samavesh garnuparcha?
Tapainko kinmel anubhavko imandar mulyankan lekhna, hamro website wa app ma 'Mero Samiksha haru' khand ma januhos ra tyaha bistrit pratikriya lekhnus.	Mero kinmel anubhavko imandar mulyankan kaha lekhna sakchu?

Tapaile kineko vastuko pratikriya dina, hamro website ma 'Mero Kharid haru' khand ma januhos ra sambandhi utpadanko chheu ma 'Samiksha Lekhnus' ma click garnuhos.	Maile kineko vastuko barema pratikriya kasari dine?
Utpadanko rating ra samiksha lekhna, utpadan prishtha ma januhos ra 'Samiksha Lekhnus' button khojnuhos. Tyaha tapaile tara rating dina ra aafno bichar lekhna saknuhuncha.	Utpadanko rating ra samiksha kaha lekhna sakincha?
Arulai samanko barema batauna, hamro platform ma samiksha lekhnus. Yasle anya grahak haru lai utpadanko barema janna maddat garnecha.	Maile kineko samanko barema arulai kasari bataune?
Website ma product review lekhna, utpadan prishtha ma januhos, 'Samiksha Lekhnus' ma click garnuhos, ra aafno anubhav, rating ra tippani haru lekhnus.	Website ma product review kasari lekhne?
Tapainko kinmel anubhav sajha garna, hamro website wa app ma 'Grahak Samiksha' khand ma januhos ra tyaha aafno pratikriya lekhnus.	Mero kinmelko anubhav sajha garna chahanchu, kaha garne?
Utpadanko gunstar bare aafno bichar byakta garna, utpadan prishtha ma gayera 'Samiksha Lekhnus' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos ra imandari purwak aafno anubhav lekhnus.	Utpadanko gunstarko barema mero bichar kasari byakta garne?
Grahak pratikriya form bharna hamro website ko 'Grahak Sahayata' khand ma januhos ra tyaha 'Pratikriya Dinus' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos.	Grahak pratikriya form kaha bharne?
Photo sahitko samiksha post garna, samiksha lekhda 'Photo Upload Garnuhos' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos ra aafno photo sanglagna garnuhos.	Maile kineko samanko photo sahitko samiksha kasari post garne?
Utpadanko sakaratmak ra nakaratmak paksha haru lekhna, samiksha form ma 'Faida haru' ra 'Kami haru' khand ma aafna bichar haru lekhnus.	Utpadanko sakaratmak ra nakaratmak pakshharu kaha lekhna sakchu?
Online store ma product review lekhna, aafno khata ma login garnuhos, kineko utpadan khojnuhos, ra 'Samiksha Lekhnus' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos.	Online store ma product review lekhne tarika ke ho?
Imandar pratikriya dina, utpadanko ramro ra naramro duwai paksha haru ullekh garnuhos. Tapainko wastawik anubhav sajha garnuhos.	Mero kharid anubhavko barema imandar pratikriya kasari dine?
Tapainko sujhav lekhna, utpadan prishtha ma 'Samiksha Lekhnus' ma click garnuhos ra 'Sudhar ka lagi sujhav haru' khand ma aafna bichar haru lekhnus.	Utpadanko barema mero sujhav kaha lekhna sakchu?
Samiksha lekhda utpadanko gunstar, mulya, prayogita ra tikau pana jasta paksha haru ma dhyan dinuhos. Tapainko wastawik anubhav sajha garnuhos.	Grahak samiksha lekhda ke ke kurama dhyan dinuparcha?
Utpadanko rating dina, samiksha form ma diyeko tara pranali prayog garnuhos. 1 dekhi 5 tara samma chhanot garna saknuhuncha.	Maile kineko samanko rating kasari dine?
Tapainko bichar aru sanga baadna, samiksha lekhnu ka saathai samajik media ma pani sajha garna saknuhuncha. Hamro platform bata sidhai share garne vikalpa chhanot garnuhos.	Utpadanko barema mero bichar arusanga kasari baadne?
Samiksha ma utpadanko bisheshata haru, prayog anubhav, gunstar, mulya ko uchitata ra samagra santushti samavesh garnuhos.	Samiksha lekhda kun kun jankari samavesh garnuparcha?
Tapainko kinmel anubhavko imandar mulyankan lekhna, hamro website wa app ma 'Mero Samiksha haru' khand ma januhos ra tyaha bistrit pratikriya lekhnus.	Mero kinmel anubhavko imandar mulyankan kaha lekhna sakchu?
Tapaile kineko samanko samiksha lekhna, kripaya hamro website ma login garnuhos ra utpadan prishtha ma gayera 'Samiksha Lekhnus' button ma click garnuhos.	Maile kineko samanko samiksha kasari lekhne?
Tapainko anubhav sajha garna hamro mobile app ma januhos, utpadan khojnuhos ra 'Samiksha Lekhnus' vikalpa chhanot garnuhos.	Utpadanko barema mero anubhav kaha sajha garna sakchu?
Grahak samiksha lekhna, utpadan prishtha ma januhos, tala scroll garnuhos ra 'Aafno Anubhav Sajha Garnuhos' ma click garnuhos. Tyaspachi form bharnuhos.	Grahak samiksha lekhne prakriya ke ho?
Tapaile kineko vastuko pratikriya dina, hamro website ma 'Mero Kharid haru' khand ma januhos ra sambandhi utpadanko chheu ma 'Samiksha Lekhnus' ma click garnuhos.	Maile kineko vastuko barema pratikriya kasari dine?

price kati samma ho?	kati samma ko price cha?
minimum price kati samma ho?	price kati samma ko cha?
maximum price kati samma ho?	kum cha ke badi?
sasto ko kati samma cha?	sasto ko price kati ho?
mahango ko kati samma cha?	yesto saman ko price kati samma ho?

kum ko kati samma cha?	maximum price kati samma ho?
price kati samma range ma cha?	sasto ra mahango ko price range k ho?
mahango ra sasto ko range kati ho?	mahango cha ke sasto?
range ma kati samma ho?	mahango ko limit kati ho?

Mafi chahanchhau, shipment ma deri bhayo.	Mero shipment deri bhayo, kina?
Shipment aauna deri bhayo, maafi chahanchhau.	Shipment aauna kati din lagi sakyo, kina deri?
Order aauna thap samay lagchha, dhairyata garnuhos.	Mero order kahile samma aauchha?
Shipment tracking update huna samasya chha.	Shipment kaha pugyo, kina update chaina?
Shipment track garna link pathauna milchha.	Shipment track garna milchha ki namilne?
Deri ko karan shipment delay chha.	Shipment deri hune karan ke ho?
Tapai ko order ko status update ma samasya chha.	Mero order ko status kina update huna nasakyo?
Deri bhaye, shipment tracking update garne koshish ma chha.	Order deri huna ta milcha tara kina?
Shipment deri bhaye contact garnuhos.	Shipment deri bhaye, aba ke garne?
Shipment update pathauna samasya chha.	Mero shipment ko update kahile pathaunus?

address thik garna ko lagi hami lai samparka garnuhos	delivery address thik chhaina

Tapaiko wishlistma ke-ke chhan thaha pauna, kripaya 'Mero khata' pustrma gayera 'Wishlist' ma click garnuhos.	Mero wishlistma ke chha herna ma ke garn sakchhu?
Tapaiko wishlistma raheko vastuharuko jankari herna, kripaya 'Mero khata' pustrma gayera 'Wishlist' ma click garnuhos.	Maile wishlistma raheko vastuharu herna chahanchhu.
Tapaiko wishlistma raheko sabai vastuharu herna, kripaya 'Mero khata' pustrma gayera 'Wishlist' ma click garnuhos.	Mero wishlistma ke chha bhanera kasari thaha pauna sakchhu?

wishlist ma add garna product page ma janus ra 'Add to Wishlist' button thichnus.	wishlist ma add garnu cha, ke garnu parcha?
wishlist ma rakheko saman herna milcha hola, wishlist section ma janus.	wishlist ma rakheko saman herna milcha ki?

Thik chha, maile yo item wishlist bata hatae.	Yo item wishlist bata hataunu parcha.
Maile yo saman wishlist bata hatae.	Malai yo saman wishlist bata hatauna man parcha.
Yo bastu wishlist bata hataidiyo.	Wishlist bata yo bastu hataidinuhos.
Yo product wishlist bata hataeko chhu.	Yo product aba wishlist ma rakhna chahina.
Yo item wishlist bata remove gareko chhu.	Yo item wishlist bata remove garnuhos.
Maile yo item wishlist bata hataeko chhu.	Yo item aba wishlist bata hatau.
Yo saman wishlist bata delete gareko chhu.	Yo saman wishlist bata delete garnu parcha.
Yo product wishlist bata hataidiyo.	Wishlist bata yo product hataidinuhos.
Maile yo bastu wishlist bata hataidiyo.	Kripaya yo bastu wishlist bata hataidinuhos.
Yo product wishlist bata hataidiyo.	Yo product mero wishlist ma aba chahidaina.
Yo item aba wishlist ma chaina.	Yo item aba wishlist ma nabhaye pani huncha.
Yo bastu wishlist bata hatae.	Yo bastu wishlist bata hataunu parcha.
